 "body": "<p>A full list of the contents of the guidance on PFI is shown below. The guidance is subdivided into sections, the opening page of each section being in bold in the list below. Please click on the page number alongside to go direct to each section.</p>\n\n<p>The PFI section of the BIM does not currently contain guidance for those applying one of EU adopted IFRS and IFRIC 12, FRS 101 or FRS 102</p>\n\n<p>HMRC officers should send any requests for further guidance to BAI Business Profits.</p>\n",
